","text":"It becomes uncontrollable if it is enraged. It destroys everything with shredding claws and fire."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"It becomes uncontrollable if it is enraged. It destroys everything with shredding claws and fire."},{"version":"diamond","text":"As a result of its long-held dream of flying, its cellular structure changed, and wings grew out."},{"version":"pearl","text":"As a result of its long-held dream of flying, its cellular structure changed, and wings grew out."},{"version":"platinum","text":"As a result of its long-held dream of flying, its cellular structure changed, and wings grew out."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"It\u2019s uncontrollable if enraged. It flies around spouting flames and scorching fields and mountains."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"It\u2019s uncontrollable if enraged. It flies around spouting flames and scorching fields and mountains."},{"version":"black","text":"As a result of its long-held dream of flying, its cellular structure changed, and wings grew out."},{"version":"white","text":"As a result of its long-held dream of flying, its cellular structure changed, and wings grew out."},{"version":"black-2","text":"As a result of its long-held dream of flying, its cellular structure changed, and wings grew out."},{"version":"white-2","text":"As a result of its long-held dream of flying, its cellular structure changed, and wings grew out."},{"version":"x","text":"It becomes uncontrollable if it is enraged. It destroys everything with shredding claws and fire."},{"version":"y","text":"It\u2019s uncontrollable if enraged. It flies around spouting flames and scorching fields and mountains."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Salamence came about as a result of a strong, long-held dream of growing wings. It is said that this powerful desire triggered a sudden mutation in this Pok\u00e9mon\u2019s cells, causing it to sprout its magnificent wings."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"By evolving into Salamence, this Pok\u00e9mon finally realizes its long-held dream of growing wings. To express its joy, it flies and wheels all over the sky while spouting flames from its mouth."},{"version":"sun","text":"When angered, it loses all sense of itself and destroys everything around it. The destruction will continue until Salamence has tired itself out."},{"version":"moon","text":"It flies around on its wings, which have grown in at last. In its happiness, it gushes hot flames, burning up the fields it passes over."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"Overjoyed at finally being able to fly, it flies all over the place and usually doesn\u2019t land until it\u2019s completely exhausted and needs to sleep."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"Thanks to its fervent wishes, the cells in its body finally mutated, and at last it has its heart\u2019s desire\u2014wings."},{"version":"sword","text":"Salamence is an unusual Pok\u00e9mon in that it was able to evolve a body with wings just by constantly wishing to be able to fly."},{"version":"shield","text":"While basking in the joy of flight generally keeps this Pok\u00e9mon in high spirits, Salamence turns into an uncontrollable menace if something angers it."}],"evo":{"name":"bagon","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"shelgon","level":1,"min_level":30,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"salamence","level":2,"min_level":50,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"nee